  textComponent: {fileID: 1114233201459697456}
  lines:
  - 'To the seeker who arrives: Three islands await your presence.'
  - Three trials will test your spirit. Three stars will light your path.
  - Seek understanding in sight, action, and language.
  - When all three shine bright, the storm will part.
  - Trust the journey.
  textSpeed: 0.07
